  "text": "ER is at the center of a number of vital cellular processes, and ER functions have implications for various pathologies including cancer. ER stress is a key player of intracellular signaling pathways that govern ICD [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Most of the agents inducing ICD are targeting ER. In a recent review, Garg et al. comprehensively discuss possible strategies enabling ER stress for cancer therapy [CITATION_3] .",
